			<h3>That wasn\'t so hard, was it?  Now you are ready to use <a href="', $boardurl, '/index.php">your installation of SMF</a>.  Hope you like it!</h3>';

	if (is_writable(dirname(__FILE__)) || is_writable(__FILE__))
